de_qatar by mr-thermaltake (aka dust3d_v2)

=================================
Did a overhaul of my first released map.
Highly detailed balanced dust map
=================================
Features:
* 40 spawnpoints
* Water features giving dust maps a new feel
* 2 story structures
* Well balanced for a even fight
* Great for wars
* 3D skybox

** NAV file not included. NAV mesh just did not want to work even manually.

I give permission for anybody to create its NAV and release it.
=================================
Credits:

DaveJ as this map was based off de_dust
polymorph who helped with optimizing this map to its nipples.
Bloodscorch community for c&c'ing throught its process.

=================================
http://mr-c.vze.com
http://www.bloodscorch.com
=================================

a) Is not sold individually or part of another package
b) Is distrubuted along with the readme
c) Appropiate credits are given.
